{"tid":1542473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"絕對唔可以用自殺既義士做文宣！！","createTime":"2019-09-05T00:55:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T01:26:28.000Z","uid":201604,"like":75,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"64a222b20bc632a5f5b9750a738106a3dcaf4f1c","tid":1542473,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T00:55:15.000Z","msg":"<ins><span style=\"color: gold;\">人都死左 唔好畀佢白白犧牲</span></ins><br />\n我都相信義士唔會介意 但試諗下<br />\n自覺已經無能為力既手足 <br />\n見到每次有人輕生都會有文宣 <br />\n或者其他方法利用 佢就會諗<br />\n「既然我都冇咩做到 得自殺幫到手 唯有出埋最後一分力啦」<br />\n結果就係造成更多手足自殺<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>唔煲大佢 係咪已經麻木左</ins></span><br />\n每次睇到手足有事都會好心痛 又點會麻木<br />\n就算手足想提醒大家<br />\n但大家已經好清醒<br />\n被捕 受傷 被性侵 過世既 已經太多啦<br />\n我地唔需要手足用生命黎提醒<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: gold;\">人有選擇自殺既權利</span></ins><br />\n唔評論自殺對錯 但諗清楚<br />\n自殺對運動係有負面影響 唔會有貢獻<br />\n會打擊士氣 減少戰力 引起人仿效<br />\n又唔會對政權造成傷害<br />\n如果真係為場運動著想 請以大局為重<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n手足每一位都係缺一不可呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"7b8391fe7ae30b93189b488ca9fe4736718e5e5e","tid":1542473,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T00:56:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a15ac7fafc489ee1498cb56acefae30c32ba44ce","tid":1542473,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T00:56:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db3252173100c4ba417e97403b67aece5e46bf5c","tid":1542473,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T00:58:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"daa4b0f2dee910fc00842d24eaede67e9c2a6fe4","tid":1542473,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T00:58:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e55f97801241aca20d162bfbf633c7f925ec39c","tid":1542473,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,